unpublishedAction.name: Query1

actionConfiguration.body:
select ssd.* ,ssci.contact_number as school_contact_number,ssci.status as school_contact_number_status, ssei.email as school_mail , ssei.status as school_email_status , ssoi.academic_partners,ssoi.quality_of_website, ssoi.tentative_school_area, ssoi.general_school_feedback, ssoi.comment, ssf.class_1_fee,
ssf.class_2_fee, ssf.class_3_fee, ssf.class_4_fee, ssf.class_5_fee, ssf.class_6_fee, ssf.class_7_fee, ssf.class_8_fee, ssf.class_9_fee, ssf.class_10_fee, ssf.class_11_fee, ssf.class_12_fee, sss.tentative_school_strength, sss.class_1_strength, sss.class_2_strength, sss.class_3_strength, sss.class_4_strength, sss.class_5_strength, sss.class_6_strength, sss.class_7_strength, sss.class_8_strength, sss.class_9_strength,sss.class_10_strength,sss.class_11_strength,sss.class_12_strength, sspi.principal_id , sspi.initial, sspi.prefix, sspi.name, sspi.qualification, sspi.gender, sspi.status as principal_status,
sspei.email as principal_email, sspei.status as principal_email_status, sspci.contact_number as principal_contact_number, sspci.status as principal_contact_number_status

from cbse.sales_school_details  ssd
left join cbse.sales_school_contact_info ssci
on ssd.sales_school_id = ssci.sales_school_id
left join cbse.sales_school_email_info ssei
on ssd.sales_school_id = ssei.sales_school_id
left join cbse.sales_school_other_info ssoi
on ssd.sales_school_id = ssoi.sales_school_id
left join cbse.sales_school_fee ssf
on ssd.sales_school_id = ssf.sales_school_id
left join cbse.sales_school_strength sss
on ssd.sales_school_id = sss.sales_school_id
left join cbse.sales_principal_info sspi
on ssd.sales_school_id = sspi.sales_school_id
left join cbse.sales_principal_email_info sspei
on sspi.principal_id = sspei.principal_id
left join cbse.sales_principal_contact_info sspci
on sspi.principal_id = sspci.principal_id

invalids: 'Query timeout' field must be an integer between 0 and 60000
